<body class="bg-black">
<div class="container text-center">
        <img  src="images/dark-thinksmarter.png" style="height: 200px; width:300px;"/>
    </div>
    
<div class="container">
    <section class="h-100 gradient-form bg-transparent">
        <div class="container py-5 h-100">
            <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">
                <div class="col-xl-10">
                    <div class="card bg-dark rounded-3 text-white" style="border: 1px solid white;">
                        <div class="row g-0">
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <div class="card-body p-md-5 mx-md-4">

                                    <div class="text-center">
                                       <!-- <img src="images/smarter.png" style="width: 185px;" alt="logo">-->
                                       <br/>
                                       <br/>
                                       
                                        <h4 class="mt-1 mb-5 pb-1">Login to account</h4>
                                    </div>

                                    <form method="POST" action="/login">



                                        <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                                            <input type="email" id="form2Example11" class="form-control bg-transparent text-white" placeholder="user@email.com" name="email"/>
                                            <label class="form-label" for="form2Example11">Email</label>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                                            <input type="password" id="form2Example22" class="form-control bg-transparent text-white" placeholder=" enter password" name="password" />
                                            <label class="form-label" for="form2Example22">Password</label>
                                        </div>

                                        <p class="text-center text-danger alert"><%= LoginErrorMessage %></p> 
                                       
                            
                                       
                                          

                                        <div class="text-center pt-1 mb-5 pb-1">
                                            <button class="btn btn-outline-warning btn-block gradient-custom-2 mb-3" type="submit">Log in</button><br/>
                                            <a class="text-muted" href="/forgot">Forgot password?</a>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center pb-4">
                                            <p class="mb-0 me-2">Don't have an account?</p>
                                            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline-warning">Create new</a>
                                        </div>

                                    </form>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex  bg-dark align-items-center gradient-custom-2" >

                                <div class="text-white text-center px-3 py-4 p-md-5 mx-md-4">
                                    <!--<img src="images/smarter.png" style="height: 100%; width: 100%"/>-->
                                    <br/>
                                    <br/>
                                    <a href="#" class="fa fa-github"></a>
            <a href="#" class="fa fa-twitter"></a>
            <a href="#" class="fa fa-instagram"></a>
                                    <p class="small mb-0">
                                        It is important for every person to have a choice. Having the ability to make choices gives us the opportunity to experience what we all know as life. Throughout this research, we will discover how effective games  are at improving brain functionality. There is numerous research that suggests the stated hypothesis is valid and that games can improve your brain functionality. Finding this hypothesis to be valid, will help to pave the way for creating ways to reduce a decline in brain functionality such as memory and decision-making skills.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
